WEBVTT

00:01.360 --> 00:08.029
Today, I met a gentleman who told me – who
is an Indian, that as far as Indians are concerned

00:08.029 --> 00:09.290
they have come here to make money.

00:09.290 --> 00:10.290
Not to know God.

00:10.290 --> 00:18.160
So they are not interested in you.  And the
other people here, they won’t listen to

00:18.160 --> 00:19.160
you.

00:19.160 --> 00:22.460
They will come to your program and go away.

00:22.460 --> 00:23.760
I said- why?

00:23.760 --> 00:30.120
Because you can’t pin them down without
you get some money out of them.

00:30.120 --> 00:33.040
(Shri Mataji laughs in astonishment).

00:33.040 --> 00:36.410
I said, “how much are they going to pay
me?” He said, “Whatever you like” You

00:36.410 --> 00:37.910
must understand their psychology.

00:37.910 --> 00:40.950
If you do not take any money from them, they
won’t be bothered.

00:40.950 --> 00:42.579
You see, he told me an American psychology
which was really very shocking.

00:42.579 --> 00:47.020
He said, they talk like this- “I have paid
for this."

00:47.020 --> 00:51.320
If they have paid for it, they will go though
it whatever it is.

00:51.320 --> 00:54.510
Otherwise they will not go through it.

00:54.510 --> 00:56.910
And it was too much for me.

00:56.910 --> 00:59.110
I said- “I can’t believe it."

00:59.110 --> 01:00.300
How can that be?

01:00.300 --> 01:02.210
There are true seekers in this world.

01:02.210 --> 01:09.299
Those who are truthful seekers will understand
that you can not pay for what you have already

01:09.299 --> 01:10.850
within yourself.

01:10.850 --> 01:19.159
And this is what one has to realize that God
has built you up in such a fashion that everything

01:19.159 --> 01:20.440
is within you.

01:20.440 --> 01:23.870
You have got your spirit in your heart.

01:23.870 --> 01:30.500
As I told you before and then you have got
that vital force within you * or that divine

01:30.500 --> 01:32.320
force within you called as Kundalini.

01:32.320 --> 01:39.160
The true desire * This is the true desire.

01:39.160 --> 01:44.930
The rest of them as I told you are not true
desires as they do not give you satisfaction.

01:44.930 --> 01:50.640
So this is the true desire within you which
has to work it out and when it works out,

01:50.640 --> 01:52.790
you become yourself.

01:52.790 --> 01:58.300
Means you know what powers you have, and you
can manifest your own power.

01:58.300 --> 02:03.310
It seems very fantastic to hear that we have
all these powers within us that we can cure

02:03.310 --> 02:05.799
ourselves, we can cure others.

02:05.799 --> 02:13.330
We can cure our mental problems and we can
cure others’ mental problems.

02:13.330 --> 02:20.340
We can solve many problems of money and other
nonsensical things about which we are worried.

02:20.340 --> 02:21.440
Our priorities change.

02:21.440 --> 02:24.940
We become transformed and we become collectively
conscious.

02:24.940 --> 02:30.180
So we can treat others and we can know about
ourselves.

02:30.180 --> 02:36.530
Seems to be very fantastic but as I told you
that you are made into this beautiful body

02:36.530 --> 02:41.840
with great care and love in such a beautiful
way.

02:41.840 --> 02:43.650
I’ll show you that.

02:43.650 --> 02:46.819
Now all these centers exist within you.

02:46.819 --> 02:50.590
You need not take me for granted but they
exist.

02:50.590 --> 02:55.730
And when the kundalini rises, she passes through
all these various centers and enlightens them

02:55.730 --> 02:56.730
and nourishes them.

02:56.730 --> 03:04.220
It’s a fact that this knowledge was known
to Indians, great seers of Indians, thousands

03:04.220 --> 03:05.709
