that by praying to God, by (meditating*Unclear)

03:20.100 --> 03:24.540
themselves to God they will be able to achieve
the advent of God.

03:24.540 --> 03:27.590
So they were praying for the advent of God,
that was one sided.

03:27.590 --> 03:30.310
Left sided people as we can call it.

03:30.310 --> 03:31.310
Who worship.

03:31.310 --> 03:37.110
The right sided people are the people who
thought that it is better to excite and awaken

03:37.110 --> 03:45.840
the different elements by which we can be
benefited.

03:45.840 --> 03:48.790
And that’s how they tried to do “yagnas”(hawan).

03:48.790 --> 03:56.140
“yagnas” means a kind of a ritual by which
you can excite or by which you can use the

03:56.140 --> 03:57.180
